transcription.text:
Speaker 1: Hi, thank you so much for calling Viagra. How can I help you today?

Speaker 2: Well, I need a new supply.

Speaker 1: All righty. I can help you with this. Can I get your full name and date of birth, please?

Speaker 2: Marion Wells, 5-15-48.

Speaker 1: All right, Mr. Wells, I see your last prescription was for a quantity of 10 of the 50 mg Viagra AGV. Is that accurate?

Speaker 2: Yes, it is.

Speaker 1: And is that the refill you would like to do this time around?

Speaker 2: It is.

Speaker 1: Okay, so going to PO Box 407, Kirtland, New Mexico?

Speaker 2: 87417.

Speaker 1: All righty. And do you want me to run the same card we have on file?

Speaker 2: No.

Speaker 1: Okay. You can erase that because I've deleted that card.

Speaker 2: All righty. I can take the new card from you then when you're ready.

Speaker 1: PO Box 4037-6627-6963-0340, expiration 1-30.

Speaker 2: And then the three-digit security code?

Speaker 1: 0-1-6.

Speaker 2: I can put this through for you.

Speaker 1: All right, Mr. Wells, that went through and you're all set.

Speaker 2: Okay. Appreciate it.

Speaker 1: You're very welcome. Happy to help.

Speaker 2: Have a good day.

Speaker 1: You too. Bye-bye.
